# ccsnvim

> Shows the cheatsheet of my nvim configs

- Files finder:
`<leader> + p + f`

- Files Explorer:
`<leader> + e`

- Grep:
`<leader> + p + s`

- Undo Tree:
`<leader> + u`

- Create directory in the current path:
`<leader> + d + d`

- Create a new file (Inside the files explorer)
`a`

> ---------- HARPOON ---------- 

- Add file to harpoon:
`<leader> + a`

- Open Harpoon:
`<C-e>`

> ---------- Nvim Console Commands ----------

- Exit
`:Ex`

- Update
`:so`

- Synchronize plugins
`:DockerSync`

- Install Language Highlight
`:TSInstall`
